    <hr style="width: 75%" />
    <h2 id="programming">Do it all over again&hellip;</h2>
    <p>It is also possible to do this exercise using the spacetime program by Glen Myers. To model the first situation a layout <a href="simulator/flicker.sts">like this</a> can be created:</p>
    <p>
      <img src="flicker-highway.png" alt="" />
      <img src="flicker-events-rails.png" alt="" />
      <img src="flicker-events-slider.png" alt="" />
    </p>
    <hr style="width: 75%" />
    <p>Modeling the situation where the the pulses travel at less than the speed of light can be done <a href="simulator/sflicker.sts">like this</a>:</p>
    <p>
      <img src="sflicker-highway.png" alt="" />
      <img src="sflicker-events-rails.png" alt="" />
      <img src="sflicker-events-slider.png" alt="" />
    </p>
    <hr style="width: 75%" />
    <p>Finding the length of the bar such that there is no flicker can be done <a href="simulator/noflicker.sts">like this</a>:</p>
    <p>
